    "spineName": "",
    "link": "",
    "sound": "czdd_czcdou",
    "isOptiong": -1
  },
  {
    "id": 7,
    "words": "我……我是，我就是您的孩子！",
    "bjName": "bj_hall",
    "spineName": "main,主角,1",
    "link": "",
    "sound": "czdd_wsndhz",
    "isOptiong": -1
  },
  {
    "id": 8,
    "words": "#主角#再次流下泪来，城主此时也眼睛湿润，想要起身却无力地跌坐回座位。",
